  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA84-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu piriviṭai āṟṟāḷāya talaivi tōḻikkuc (ET: āṟṟāḷ eṉak kavaṉṟa tōḻikkut talaivi) colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what SHE, was was unable to bear it during the separation, said to [her] confidante.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA84">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            kaṇṇun tōḷun taṇṇaṟuṅ katuppun</l>
<l>            titalai yalkulum palapā rāṭṭi</l>
<l>            nerunalu mivaṇar maṉṉē yiṉṟē</l>
<l>            perunī roppiṟ pēey veṇṭēr</l>
<l>            maraṉi ṉīḷiṭai māṉacai yuṟūuñ </l>
<l>            cuṭumaṭ ṭacumpiṉ mattan tiṉṟa</l>
<l>            piṟavā veṇṇai yuruppiṭat taṉṉa</l>
<l>            yuvareḻu kaḷari yōmaiyaṅ kāṭṭu</l>
<l>            veyilvīṟ ṟirunta vempalai yaruñcura</l>
<l>            mēkuva reṉpa tāmē tamvayi </l>
<l>            ṉirantōr māṟṟa lāṟṟā</l>
<l>            villiṉ vāṭkai vallā tōrē.</l>
        </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Even yesterday he [was] here indeed,</l>
<l rend="indent3">praising in many [words my] eyes and shoulders</l>
<l rend="indent3">and cool fragrant hair and hips with beauty spots.</l>
<l rend="indent4">Today,</l>
<l>he himself says he will go<note place="foot">Here the <term xml:lang="ta">tāmē</term> indicates that we have to take the <term xml:lang="ta">eṉpa</term> not in the usual sense of general saying, but that HE is the speaker.</note></l>
<l rend="indent">through the difficult desert afflicted with heat, where the sunlight was</l>
<l rend="indent2">enormous on the wilderness of Ōmai trees in the saline soil,</l>
<l rend="indent3">where the saltishness rises as within the heat of unfinished butter</l>
<l rend="indent3">eaten by the churning stick in the earthen pot,</l>
<l rend="indent3">where the mirage of an evil spirit makes the deer yearning</l>
<l rend="indent3">on the treeless long way with the resemblance of great water,</l>
<l>– he who hasn't the strength for a living in the house</l>
<l rend="indent">without being able to refuse beggars [come] to his place.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
